'''2017年[[世界輕艇激流錦標賽|世界輕艇激流錦標賽]]'''是[[國際輕艇總會|國際輕艇總會]]（ICF）主辦的第三十八屆世界輕艇激流錦標賽，於2017年9月22日至10月1日在[[法國|法國]][[波城|波城]]的{{link-en|波城-比利牛斯體育場|Pau-Pyrénées Whitewater Stadium}}舉行<ref>{{cite web|title=Canoe Slalom Calendar|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/event-calendar|publisher=[[國際輕艇總會|國際輕艇總會]]|accessdate=2013-06-29|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123130500/https://www.canoeicf.com/event-calendar|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Pau set to host biggest slalom and wildwater World Championships ever|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/news/pau-set-host-biggest-slalom-and-wildwater-world-championships-ever|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=2017-09-26|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123152132/https://www.canoeicf.com/news/pau-set-host-biggest-slalom-and-wildwater-world-championships-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本屆賽事新增男女混合加拿大式雙人艇（C2）和極限愛斯基摩艇（Extreme K1）項目<ref>{{cite web|title=Estanguet urges canoe slalom to be bold to guarantee future growth|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/news/estanguet-urges-canoe-slalom-be-bold-guarantee-future-growth|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=2017-09-26|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122191331/https://www.canoeicf.com/news/estanguet-urges-canoe-slalom-be-bold-guarantee-future-growth|dead-url=no}}</ref>， 男女混合加拿大式雙人艇項目是自從{{link-en|1981年世界輕艇激流錦標賽|1981 ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships|1981年}}以來再度進入賽會，男子加拿大式雙人艇（C2）團體項目則因只有四隊參賽而不列入正式比賽<ref>{{cite web|title=INTERNATIONAL CANOE FEDERATION CANOE SLALOM COMPETITION RULES 2017|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/sites/default/files/canoe_slalom_competition_rules_2017_rev_csl_final_inclcslx_4.pdf|accessdate=2017-09-26|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122092229/https://www.canoeicf.com/sites/default/files/canoe_slalom_competition_rules_2017_rev_csl_final_inclcslx_4.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

